274
00:18:58,480 --> 00:18:59,360
Cái gì?

275
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:02,250
Sakuragi Hanamichi.

276
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,800
Ayako.

277
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:07,710
Khi tôi cho rằng chân của Akagi
